Class SVGCalculator

java.lang.Object
org.tquadrat.foundation.svg.type.SVGCalculator
@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: SVGCalculator.java 1140 2024-06-23 11:17:41Z tquadrat $") @API(status=STABLE, since="0.4.7") @UtilityClass public final class SVGCalculator extends Object

The class SVGCalculator provide functions to perform calculations on instances of SVGNumber and its subclasses.
